---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Services - Damien Herlihy">
  <section class="services-page container page-content">
    <h1>Services</h1>

    <div class="services-prose">
      <p>
        I'm something of a personal knowledge management (PKM) nerd. Without any
        particular ranking, Marie Kondo, David Allen, Marie Poulin, and Tiago
        Forte have been my guiding lights in this space. In the area of PKM my
        go-to-tool is <a href="https://www.notion.com/" target="_blank" class="link">Notion</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>What is Notion?</h2>
      <p>
        It's a single space where you can think, write, and plan. Notion is like
        building with LEGO blocks: you can easily assemble, rearrange, and
        customize anything in it, unlike a traditional Word document, which is
        more like a fixed, printed page.
      </p>

      <h3>Let me tell you.</h3>
      <p>
        I've made Notion my life for the past year, so you don't have to! During
        that year I created a range of templates that run my business, and my
        life too. I share what I've learned through two main services: templates
        and one-to-one coaching.
      </p>

      <h2>Templates</h2>
      <p>
        My paid and free templates are found at <a href="https://www.languagelayouts.com/" target="_blank" class="link">Language Layouts</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Coaching</h2>
      <p>
        Also, I do coaching. I help teachers get organised. We cover the core
        ideas of PKM and at the end of it all you'll have a one of a kind Notion
        workspace. Something you can use to organise your teaching business
        online. I charge 999 USD dollars for this experience. I only have six
        slots per year. As this is a new service, my first three clients will get
        this service for $500 USD.
      </p>

      <h3>Why is this a good deal?</h3>
      <p>
        I'm the type of person who always wants to please. Owing to that
        embedded personality trait I will always provide you with significantly
        more value than what you have paid.
      </p>
      <p>
        Also, I'm in a sweet spot in terms of my experience. I have built a
        successful language school, I have an extensive knowledge of PKM, and I
        have invested one year to become highly proficient in Notion.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you are interested in this service contact me below and we can chat.
        Plus, I can share some extra documents about the coaching experience too.
      </p>

      <h3>Oh!</h3>
      <p>
        One more thing. I'm moving onto my '<a href="https://www.amazon.com/Second-Mountain-David-Brooks/dp/0812993268" target="_blank" class="link">Second Mountain</a>'. After taking care
        of running expenses, all proceeds I earn from this venture will be
        donated to charity. My aim is to commit 10% of my overall income - across
        all my businesses - to charity.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-contact">
      <ContactForm />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .services-prose {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .services-prose h2 {
    margin-top: 2em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }

  .services-prose h3 {
    margin-top: 1.5em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }

  .services-prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.2em;
  }

  .services-contact {
    margin-top: 48px;
    max-width: 700px;
  }
</style>
